data.text:
Louis Joel "Lewis" Woodbury

Born 29 Aug 1900 in Gloucester, Essex, Massachusetts, USA

Ancestors

Husband of Alma Corinna (Fredette) Woodbury — married 1921 in Arlington, Middlesex, Massachusetts, United States

Descendants

Died 24 Oct 1971 at age 71 in Hollywood, Dade, Florida, United States

Profile last modified 26 Nov 2022 | Created 3 Mar 2018

This page has been accessed 215 times.

Biography

Louis Joel Woodbury was born on 29 Aug 1900 in Gloucester, Essex, Massachusetts.[1] He died on 24 Oct 1971 in Hollywood, Dade, Florida. [2] [3] [4] He is buried in the North Cambridge Catholic Cemetery, in North Cambridge, Middlesex County, Massachusetts, USA. [5]

Louis was one of the four Woodbury brothers that married one of the four Fredette sisters.

He lived in Cambridge, Massachusetts from 1921 until at least 1940.[6][7][8]
